}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#0da5df4278ce158c10f84441868afc05>.
<#0da5df4278ce158c10f84441868afc05> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/9d8a1894-9f6c-4d74-9d2e-d481f8737ced>;
