<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/2ef48b70-7d1f-11ed-a51b-432755aaeed3> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://www.smhi.se/data/utforskaren-oppna-data/hydrolog_smhi.se>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-download-hydroobs.smhi.se/api/version/latest/parameter/3.json>, <https://opendata.smhi.se/hydroobs/api>, <https://www.smhi.se/data/hitta-data-for-en-plats/ladda-ner-observationer-fran-sjoar-och-vattendrag/waterLevel>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2022-12-16"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
