<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#d741357c714176f96dcb526de1fd33b2>.
<#d741357c714176f96dcb526de1fd33b2> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/be9d3f7b-2fbc-4dca-92f9-baee027a3f89>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-05-13T07:03:00.351Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
