    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__8487.
_:b0__8487 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/67ad17749d8af23e7f8daa847d924b19>;
