_:b0__9478 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((11.00 69.00,26.00 69.00,26.00 55.00,11.00 55.00,11.00 69.00))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
