<#d10088dbe35151a857af605129837d2d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://resources.stockholm.se/data/69f1c091-d83a-4bdc-ad5d-e8a4805d6562>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-05-13T07:03:01.600Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
