<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#8d675ed58eb1b6a41cc238545ad28088>.
<#8d675ed58eb1b6a41cc238545ad28088> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://doi.org/10.5878/002640>;
