    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://doi.org/10.5878/001580> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#9332d45c54ce7b8bde7fca56c49b307b>.
<#9332d45c54ce7b8bde7fca56c49b307b> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://metadatakatalog.huddinge.se/store/26/resource/380>;
