    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "A GeoJSON file containing bicycle measurements in Gävle Municipality.\n\nAttribute data:\n\nID (Site ID)\nNAME (Site name)\nADDRESS (Site address)\nDATEUPDATED (Date of API-call)\nTIMEUPDATED  (Time of API-call in the format HHMMSS)\nLAT\nLONG\nPASSAGECONTROLLER_ID (Passage controller ID)\nPASSAGECONTROLLER_NAME (Passage controller name)\nPASSAGECONTROLLER_COUNT_TODAY (Passage controller count today)\nPASSAGECONTROLLER_COUNT_YEAR (Passage controller count year)\n\nThe coordinate system is WGS84."@en, "En GeoJSON fil som innehåller cykelmätningar inom Gävle kommun. Attributdata:\n\nID (Site ID)\nNAME (Site name)\nADDRESS (Site address)\nDATEUPDATED (Datum som API-anropet gjordes)\nTIMEUPDATED (Klockslag enligt HHMMSS som API-anropet gjordes)\nLAT\nLONG\nPASSAGECONTROLLER_ID (Passage controller ID)\nPASSAGECONTROLLER_NAME (Passage controller name)\nPASSAGECONTROLLER_COUNT_TODAY (Passage controller count today)\nPASSAGECONTROLLER_COUNT_YEAR (Passage controller count year)\n\nKoordinatsystemet är WGS84.."@sv;
